___NOTES___

Self-contained "HelloGekko UTM tracker". Runs entirely in the GTM sandbox:
captures UTM/click-id parameters from the URL, stores first- and last-touch in a
first-party cookie, restores them into the address bar via history.replaceState
(so they persist across navigation without touching the DOM or loading any
external script), and pushes them to the dataLayer. Consent is left to the tag's
own Consent Settings.
